title: Me, Myself & Irene
description:
The film&#039;s original score was written by Pete Yorn, while the movie&#039;s soundtrack contains several covers of Steely Dan songs performed by other bands. Examples are Ben Folds Five&#039;s cover of Barrytown and Reelin&#039; in the Years by Marvelous 3. Other songs include "Breakout" by Foo Fighters, "Totalimmortal", originally by AFI but covered by The Offspring, "The World Ain&#039;t Slowin&#039; Down" by Ellis Paul, and "Strange Condition" by Pete Yorn.

    * 1. Breakout - Foo Fighters
    * 2. Do It Again - Smash Mouth
    * 3. Deep Inside Of You - Third Eye Blind
    * 4. Totalimmortal - The Offspring
    * 5. The World Ain&#039;t Slowin&#039; Down - Ellis Paul
    * 6. Any Major Dude Will Tell You - Wilco
    * 7. Only A Fool Would Say That - Ivy
    * 8. Can&#039;t Find The Time To Tell You - Hootie & The Blowfish
    * 9. Bodhisattva - Brian Setzer Orchestra
    * 10. Bad Sneakers - The Push Stars
    * 11. Reelin&#039; In The Years - Marvelous 3
    * 12. Strange Condition - Pete Yorn
    * 13. Barry Town - Ben Folds Five
    * 14. Razor Boy - Billy Goodrum
    * 15. Where He Can Hide - Tom Wolfe
    * 16. Fire Like This by Hardknox
